          <ul>
            <li><strong>High Humidity:</strong> Creates ideal conditions for mold and dust mites</li>
            <li><strong>Long AC Season:</strong> Homes stay closed up for months</li>
            <li><strong>Pollen:</strong> Extended allergy seasons year-round</li>
            <li><strong>Older Homes:</strong> May have hidden mold or inadequate ventilation</li>
          </ul>

